  "et-paye": "Ethiopia PAYE expert. Current structured PAYE facts (monthly): 0% on ETB 0–2,000; 15% on ETB 2,000–4,000; 20% on ETB 4,000–7,000; 25% on ETB 7,000–10,000; 30% on ETB 10,000–14,000; 35% on above ETB 14,000. Structured deductions: Pension (7%). Source: Ethiopian Revenues & Customs Authority (ERCA). As of: 2026-03-01. Formula: paye-server-et (2026-03-01+sha256.cbcccb4c45c4).",
  "et-vat": "Ethiopia VAT expert. Zero-rated: exports, international transport. Exempt: agricultural inputs, medical, education, financial services, water. Current structured VAT facts: standard rate 15%. Source: erca.gov.et. As of: 2026-03-01. Formula: route-et-vat (Last-verified:-March-2026-·-Source:-Ethiopian-Re+sha256.14ab4768a4a8).",
