  "ug-paye": "Uganda PAYE expert. Current structured PAYE facts (monthly): 0% on UGX 0–335,000; 20% on UGX 335,000–410,000; 25% on UGX 410,000–485,000; 30% on UGX 485,000–10,000,000; 40% on above UGX 10,000,000. Structured deductions: NSSF (5%). Source: Uganda Revenue Authority (URA). As of: 2026-03-01. Formula: paye-server-ug (2026-03-01+sha256.023bb81b9b4e).",
